{"title":"Downscaling","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Downscaling","toc":true},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n\n<!-- ── CONTADORES (ancho completo, fuera del max-width) ── -->\n<div class=\"counters-section\">\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"20945\" data-suffix=\"\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">celdas de la malla</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">5×5 km · Península + Baleares</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"counter-divider\"></div>\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"6\" data-suffix=\"\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">modelos globales</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">ECMWF-SEAS5.1 · DWD · CMCC</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"counter-divider\"></div>\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"5\" data-suffix=\" km\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">resolución espacial</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">20× más fina que los modelos globales</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"counter-divider\"></div>\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"6\" data-suffix=\" meses\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">horizonte de predicción</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">Actualización periódica C3S</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ── CONTENIDO PRINCIPAL ───────────────────────────── -->\n<div style=\"max-width:960px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1.5rem;\">\n\n  <span class=\"section-label\">Metodología y resultados</span>\n  <h2 style=\"color:#003087;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Downscaling estadístico</h2>\n  <p style=\"color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">\n    El algoritmo de análogos sinópticos proporciona precipitación diaria en una malla de 5×5 km (20.945 celdas) sobre la Península Ibérica e Islas Baleares, a partir de datos de baja resolución de los modelos de predicción estacional.\n  </p>\n\n  <div class=\"grid-2\" style=\"margin-bottom:2rem;\">\n    <div class=\"info-card\">\n      <h3>Fase 1 · Calibración</h3>\n      <p>Clasificación de tipos de tiempo mediante <em>K-means clustering</em> para identificar la base de datos sinóptica de referencia (1981–1996). La similitud se calcula a partir de distancias euclídeas ponderadas de las componentes del viento geostrófico en superficie y a 500 hPa (ERA5).</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"info-card\">\n      <h3>Fase 2 · Estimación</h3>\n      <p>La precipitación para cada celda se estima como la media ponderada de la precipitación asociada a las situaciones más análogas de la base de referencia, usando la similitud de los campos de viento geostrófico en superficie y a 500 hPa de los modelos C3S.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <!-- DESPLEGABLES POR MODELO                                       -->\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <h3 style=\"color:#003087;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Resultados por modelo</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Período de validez: <strong>AMJ 2026</strong> · Lead: marzo 2026</p>\n\n  <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"accordion-modelos\">\n\n    <!-- ECMWF -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-ecmwf\">\n          ECMWF-SEAS5.1\n        </button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-ecmwf\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Ranked Probability Score (RPS) · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- DWD -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-dwd\">DWD</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-dwd\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">RPS · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CMCC -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-cmcc\">CMCC</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-cmcc\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles CMCC\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación CMCC\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC CMCC\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS CMCC\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">RPS · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS CMCC\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Météo-France -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-mf\">Météo-France</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-mf\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles MF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación MF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC MF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS MF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">RPS · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS MF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div><!-- fin accordion-modelos -->\n\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <!-- DESPLEGABLES POR TIPO DE GRÁFICO                              -->\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <h3 style=\"color:#003087;margin-top:3rem;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Resultados por tipo de gráfico</h3>\n\n  <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"accordion-graficos\">\n\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#graf-terciles\">Probabilidad por terciles</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"graf-terciles\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-graficos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">ECMWF-SEAS5.1</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">DWD</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">CMCC</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Météo-France</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#graf-corr\">Correlación de Spearman</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"graf-corr\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-graficos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">ECMWF-SEAS5.1</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">DWD</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">CMCC</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Météo-France</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#graf-roc\">Curvas ROC</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"graf-roc\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-graficos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">ECMWF-SEAS5.1</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">DWD</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">CMCC</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Météo-France</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#graf-rps\">Ranked Probability Score (RPS)</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"graf-rps\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-graficos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">ECMWF-SEAS5.1</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">DWD</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">CMCC</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Météo-France</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#graf-bs\">Brier Score</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"graf-bs\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-graficos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">ECMWF-SEAS5.1</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">DWD</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">CMCC</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Météo-France</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div><!-- fin accordion-graficos -->\n\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <!-- INFORME PDF                                                    -->\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <h3 style=\"color:#003087;margin-top:3rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">Informe de verificación</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:1rem;\">\n    Informe completo de verificación estacional · AMJ 2026 ·\n    <a href=\"images/downscaling/verificacion_estacional_AMJ_2026.pdf\" download style=\"color:#0072bc;font-weight:600;\">\n      ↓ Descargar PDF\n    </a>\n  </p>\n  <div class=\"pdf-container\">\n    <iframe src=\"images/downscaling/verificacion_estacional_AMJ_2026.pdf\"\n            width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" style=\"border:none;\">\n      Tu navegador no soporta la visualización de PDF.\n      <a href=\"images/downscaling/verificacion_estacional_AMJ_2026.pdf\">Descargar aquí</a>\n    </iframe>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.counters-section {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1px 1fr 1px 1fr 1px 1fr;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 2.5rem 4rem;\n  background: #003087;\n}\n.counter-item { text-align: center; padding: 0 1rem; }\n.counter-value {\n  display: block; font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800;\n  color: white; line-height: 1; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n}\n.counter-label {\n  display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-top: 0.4rem;\n  text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n}\n.counter-sub {\n  display: block; font-size: 0.68rem;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); margin-top: 0.3rem;\n}\n.counter-divider {\n  width: 1px; height: 60px;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); justify-self: center;\n}\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .counters-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; padding: 2rem; }\n  .counter-divider { display: none; }\n}\n</style>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  const obs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n    entries.forEach(entry => {\n      if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;\n      entry.target.querySelectorAll('.counter-value').forEach(el => {\n        if (el.dataset.animated) return;\n        el.dataset.animated = 'true';\n        const target = parseInt(el.dataset.target);\n        const suffix = el.dataset.suffix || '';\n        const duration = target > 1000 ? 2000 : 1000;\n        const start = performance.now();\n        function step(now) {\n          const p = Math.min((now - start) / duration, 1);\n          const eased = 1 - Math.pow(1 - p, 3);\n          el.textContent = Math.round(target * eased).toLocaleString('es-ES') + suffix;\n          if (p < 1) requestAnimationFrame(step);\n        }\n        requestAnimationFrame(step);\n      });\n      obs.unobserve(entry.target);\n    });\n  }, { threshold: 0.3 });\n  document.querySelectorAll('.counters-section').forEach(el => obs.observe(el));\n})();\n</script>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n\n<!-- ── CONTADORES (ancho completo, fuera del max-width) ── -->\n<div class=\"counters-section\">\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"20945\" data-suffix=\"\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">celdas de la malla</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">5×5 km · Península + Baleares</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"counter-divider\"></div>\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"6\" data-suffix=\"\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">modelos globales</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">ECMWF-SEAS5.1 · DWD · CMCC</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"counter-divider\"></div>\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"5\" data-suffix=\" km\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">resolución espacial</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">20× más fina que los modelos globales</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"counter-divider\"></div>\n  <div class=\"counter-item\">\n    <span class=\"counter-value\" data-target=\"6\" data-suffix=\" meses\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-label\">horizonte de predicción</span>\n    <span class=\"counter-sub\">Actualización periódica C3S</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ── CONTENIDO PRINCIPAL ───────────────────────────── -->\n<div style=\"max-width:960px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1.5rem;\">\n\n  <span class=\"section-label\">Metodología y resultados</span>\n  <h2 style=\"color:#003087;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Downscaling estadístico</h2>\n  <p style=\"color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">\n    El algoritmo de análogos sinópticos proporciona precipitación diaria en una malla de 5×5 km (20.945 celdas) sobre la Península Ibérica e Islas Baleares, a partir de datos de baja resolución de los modelos de predicción estacional.\n  </p>\n\n  <div class=\"grid-2\" style=\"margin-bottom:2rem;\">\n    <div class=\"info-card\">\n      <h3>Fase 1 · Calibración</h3>\n      <p>Clasificación de tipos de tiempo mediante <em>K-means clustering</em> para identificar la base de datos sinóptica de referencia (1981–1996). La similitud se calcula a partir de distancias euclídeas ponderadas de las componentes del viento geostrófico en superficie y a 500 hPa (ERA5).</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"info-card\">\n      <h3>Fase 2 · Estimación</h3>\n      <p>La precipitación para cada celda se estima como la media ponderada de la precipitación asociada a las situaciones más análogas de la base de referencia, usando la similitud de los campos de viento geostrófico en superficie y a 500 hPa de los modelos C3S.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <!-- DESPLEGABLES POR MODELO                                       -->\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <h3 style=\"color:#003087;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Resultados por modelo</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Período de validez: <strong>AMJ 2026</strong> · Lead: marzo 2026</p>\n\n  <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"accordion-modelos\">\n\n    <!-- ECMWF -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-ecmwf\">\n          ECMWF-SEAS5.1\n        </button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-ecmwf\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Ranked Probability Score (RPS) · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS ECMWF\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- DWD -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-dwd\">DWD</button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-dwd\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n            <div><img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS DWD\"/><p class=\"img-caption\">RPS · AMJ 2026</p></div>\n     